---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Tech Experiments">
  <Header />
  <main class="main">
    <article class="about">
      <h1>About This Site</h1>

      <p>
        This is a collection of experimental mini applications, tools, and creative
        coding projects. It's a space for trying out new ideas, learning new technologies,
        and building things for fun.
      </p>

      <h2>The Approach</h2>
      <p>
        Each experiment lives in its own folder, ranging from simple HTML/CSS/JS pages
        to more complex React applications. The goal is zero-friction creation:
        have an idea, build it, deploy it.
      </p>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Monorepo</strong> - pnpm workspaces + Turborepo</li>
        <li><strong>Showcase Site</strong> - Astro (static site generation)</li>
        <li><strong>Apps</strong> - Varies by project (static HTML, React, etc.)</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting</strong> - GitHub Pages</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Find more of my work at <a href="https://kevinhyde.com">kevinhyde.com</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .about {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #00d4ff;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    color: #c0c0c0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    color: #c0c0c0;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '>';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  li strong {
    color: #fff;
  }
</style>
